name: Qimberly Gaitag-Delio
content: Qimberly Gaitag-Delio, known by the nickname The Devourer, was a Qiraash female attorney who was the granddaughter of Doffen Gaitag, the founder of the luxury space station the Wheel. At some point prior to the outbreak of the Clone Wars, Delio represented the businessman Iaco Stark in a lawsuit against Dominic Raynor, the incumbent administrator of the Wheel.
